<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/672980-is-this-book-actually-any-good-i-ve-heard">Is this book actually any good? I&#39;ve heard of cats being left in jackets and handcuffs on a stumped arm... I&#39;m torn between a good fantasy series and mysterious inconsistencies. I&#39;d rather not waste time poor oversights and useless prattle.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_672980'><a id="like_count_community_question_672980" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/672980?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F91981.The_Dragonbone_Chair">like</a></span>

