          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A piece of writing is a trap,” he said cheerily, “and the best kind. A book, you see, is the only kind of trap that keeps its captive—which is knowledge—alive forever.&rdquo;</span>
